snippet.title: The Upper Hand [Fangame] - UNDEREVENT Trailer
snippet.description:
Dive into the capitalist utopia of New Yolk and engage in the short story of Sockswald. Building up to the climactic fist-clenching bossfight against HANDROMEDA.
Coming in 2025. Stay tuned for more updates
